00:29.440 --> 00:30.800
<font color="white">MATURE JENNY: </font><font color="yellow">'The River Thames</font>

00:30.800 --> 00:34.600
<font color="yellow">'pulsed through the heart of</font>
<font color="yellow">the East End like its blood,</font>

00:34.600 --> 00:36.200
<font color="yellow">'sustaining its people</font>

00:36.200 --> 00:39.560
<font color="yellow">'and taking with it much</font>
<font color="yellow">they had thrown away or lost.</font>

00:41.960 --> 00:44.400
<font color="yellow">'For some, it marked</font>
<font color="yellow">beginning of a journey.</font>

00:44.400 --> 00:47.520
<font color="yellow">'For others,</font>
<font color="yellow">it became a channel of return,</font>

00:47.520 --> 00:51.760
<font color="yellow">'bringing back the missing</font>
<font color="yellow">and the loved,</font>

00:51.760 --> 00:55.120
<font color="yellow">'the forgotten, and the longed for.</font>

00:56.800 --> 01:02.200
<font color="yellow">'It was often an escape route</font>
<font color="yellow">and sometimes the road home.'</font>

01:03.280 --> 01:05.600
<font color="white">Oi, you've got enough there to feed</font>
<font color="white">an army, Mrs Lacey!</font>

01:05.600 --> 01:08.040
<font color="cyan">That's right, see you Thursday.</font>

01:08.040 --> 01:09.680
<font color="white">MAN: What d'you say?</font>

01:09.680 --> 01:12.040
<font color="lime">I think you've got yourself</font>
<font color="lime">a deal, my son!</font>

01:12.040 --> 01:14.440
<font color="white">Good. Enjoy it.</font>

01:14.440 --> 01:15.600
<font color="lime">I will.</font>

01:15.600 --> 01:17.560
<font color="white">It's all yours. </font><font color="lime">Lovely.</font>

01:20.200 --> 01:23.520
<font color="lime">Arthur, look at that.</font>
<font color="lime">What d'you reckon, hey?</font>

01:23.520 --> 01:25.880
<font color="cyan">Speedy Gonzalez here, look!</font>

01:33.120 --> 01:35.680
<font color="white">I'm wondering what</font>
<font color="white">to do about my room.</font>

01:35.680 --> 01:37.760
<font color="cyan">Fresh flowers and new curtains?</font>

01:37.760 --> 01:40.600
<font color="white">I mean with Nurse Noakes</font>
<font color="white">and her husband coming to stay.</font>

01:40.600 --> 01:43.640
<font color="white">It's only right Chummy should have</font>
<font color="white">her old room back.</font>

01:43.640 --> 01:47.040
<font color="yellow">Chummy wouldn't dream of it.</font>
<font color="yellow">That's your room now.</font>

01:47.040 --> 01:49.600
<font color="yellow">I think Fred's clearing out</font>
<font color="yellow">another room, anyway.</font>

01:49.600 --> 01:52.600
<font color="cyan">And they might be with us for</font>
<font color="cyan">a while before they're rehoused.</font>

01:52.600 --> 01:54.720
<font color="cyan">Their whole block was condemned.</font>

01:56.800 --> 01:58.080
<font color="yellow">Jane?</font>

01:59.120 --> 02:00.200
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

02:00.200 --> 02:04.440
<font color="white">I suppose I was here to fill a gap,</font>
<font color="white">really, and, well,</font>

02:04.440 --> 02:06.360
<font color="white">that gap was Nurse Noakes.</font>

02:06.360 --> 02:10.000
<font color="white">So, I'm wondering what</font>
<font color="white">I do now there won't be a gap.</font>

02:10.000 --> 02:13.400
<font color="yellow">Jane, you're part of Nonnatus.</font>
<font color="yellow">In your own right,</font>

02:13.400 --> 02:14.800
<font color="yellow">not filling a gap.</font>

02:14.800 --> 02:19.160
<font color="lime">Quite impossible, anyway, as you'll</font>
<font color="lime">see when she arrives next week.</font>

02:19.160 --> 02:23.200
<font color="cyan">Though to be quite blunt, her</font>
<font color="cyan">grasp of timing is a little loose.</font>

02:31.800 --> 02:36.000
<font color="lime">And we pray for the continued</font>
<font color="lime">recovery of Sister Bernadette.</font>

02:36.000 --> 02:40.160
<font color="lime">May the Lord keep her safe. Amen.</font>
<font color="cyan">Amen. </font><font color="white">Amen.</font>

02:54.520 --> 02:56.800
<font color="cyan">Come on, push. Good boys.</font>

03:00.200 --> 03:01.880
<font color="cyan">Up we go.</font>

03:06.160 --> 03:11.840
<font color="cyan">Ladies, your carriage awaits.</font>

03:11.840 --> 03:13.240
<font color="white">Courtesy of our successful fete</font>

03:13.240 --> 03:15.720
<font color="white">and the generous contribution</font>
<font color="white">from the Mother House.</font>

03:15.720 --> 03:17.360
<font color="lime">A Bumblebee for a staff vehicle.</font>

03:17.360 --> 03:20.160
<font color="lime">I've had my eye on a weekend</font>
<font color="lime">in Southend for months.</font>

03:20.160 --> 03:22.120
<font color="yellow">I don't believe we cover Southend.</font>

03:22.120 --> 03:25.240
<font color="yellow">The new addition is</font>
<font color="yellow">for the carrying of gas and air.</font>

03:25.240 --> 03:29.120
<font color="yellow">And we may also appreciate the lack</font>
<font color="yellow">of pedalling in the years to come.</font>

03:29.120 --> 03:32.320
<font color="white">Speak for yourself.</font>
<font color="white">In your own time, Nurse Miller.</font>

03:32.320 --> 03:34.560
<font color="yellow">Chocks away then! </font><font color="cyan">No, no, no, no.</font>

03:34.560 --> 03:37.760
<font color="cyan">This machine is to be treated</font>
<font color="cyan">with the greatest respect.</font>

03:37.760 --> 03:39.800
<font color="cyan">Set off on this unprepared</font>

03:39.800 --> 03:43.360
<font color="cyan">and unschooled in its</font>
<font color="cyan">mechanical workings - disaster.</font>

03:43.360 --> 03:44.520
<font color="cyan">Thank you.</font>

03:44.520 --> 03:45.800
<font color="white">HORN TOOTS</font>

03:45.800 --> 03:47.240
<font color="cyan">Don't do that.</font>

03:47.240 --> 03:49.920
<font color="white">PHONE RINGS</font>

04:01.040 --> 04:03.520
<font color="cyan">Nonnatus House.</font>

04:03.520 --> 04:06.600
<font color="white">'It's my Rose. She's having it.</font>
<font color="white">She's having it now.'</font>

04:06.600 --> 04:10.040
<font color="cyan">A flower was offered to me,</font>

04:10.040 --> 04:13.160
<font color="cyan">such a flower as May never more.</font>

04:13.160 --> 04:16.440
<font color="cyan">But I said,</font>
<font color="cyan">"I have a pretty rose tree."</font>

04:16.440 --> 04:18.920
<font color="cyan">And I passed the sweet flower o'er.</font>

04:20.279 --> 04:22.360
<font color="white">'What the hell?'</font>
<font color="white">SHE GIGGLES</font>

04:22.360 --> 04:26.160
<font color="cyan">Dear fellow, do not</font>
<font color="cyan">take fright at poetry.</font>

04:27.960 --> 04:30.320
<font color="cyan">Let us start with a name</font>
<font color="cyan">and address.</font>

04:30.320 --> 04:32.360
<font color="white">'My wife. Mrs Laidlaw.</font>

04:32.360 --> 04:35.240
<font color="white">'We're at ten</font>
<font color="white">Dublin Lane off Pollard Road.</font>

04:35.240 --> 04:36.280
<font color="white">'That's ten...'</font>

04:39.120 --> 04:43.040
<font color="yellow">Sister Monica Joan, was that</font>
<font color="yellow">the telephone I just heard?</font>

04:43.040 --> 04:46.840
<font color="cyan">Child, how can I possibly</font>
<font color="cyan">interpret the working of your ears?</font>

04:48.280 --> 04:52.240
<font color="yellow">Mrs Laidlaw. Ten Dublin Lane.</font>
<font color="yellow">Right on time.</font>

04:52.240 --> 04:56.040
<font color="yellow">I have to say, your note-taking</font>
<font color="yellow">is quite exceptional.</font>

04:56.040 --> 04:58.960
<font color="lime">Do remember, the telephone</font>
<font color="lime">should only be answered</font>

04:58.960 --> 05:02.160
<font color="lime">by midwives on call.</font>
<font color="lime">It may confuse matters otherwise.</font>

05:03.280 --> 05:06.000
<font color="cyan">If matters are so easily confused...</font>

05:27.720 --> 05:30.000
<font color="white">I could murder a bit</font>
<font color="white">of steak and kidney.</font>

05:31.200 --> 05:32.960
<font color="white">Mr John Lacey among you?</font>

05:32.960 --> 05:35.160
<font color="lime">Bring me a beer. Useless wretch!</font>

05:35.160 --> 05:36.360
<font color="yellow">That's the gentleman.</font>

05:36.360 --> 05:38.640
<font color="white">"Gentleman", you say?</font>
<font color="cyan">Out the back.</font>

05:40.800 --> 05:42.640
<font color="white">But John, the sister's coming.</font>

05:42.640 --> 05:44.080
<font color="lime">What bloody sister?</font>

05:46.600 --> 05:48.040
<font color="lime">Who the hell are you?</font>

05:48.040 --> 05:49.200
<font color="white">The bloody sister!</font>

05:50.320 --> 05:52.480
<font color="lime">The doctor ain't got the guts</font>
<font color="lime">to tell me, eh?</font>

05:52.480 --> 05:55.840
<font color="lime">Sends you? Go on then, say it.</font>

05:55.840 --> 05:57.040
<font color="lime">I'm dying, ain't I?</font>

05:57.040 --> 05:59.920
<font color="white">You've got diabetes,</font>
<font color="white">I'm here to test your pee.</font>

06:01.080 --> 06:02.280
<font color="white">Lame or on the game -</font>

06:02.280 --> 06:04.440
<font color="white">only ones who should still be in bed</font>
<font color="white">this time of day.</font>

06:04.440 --> 06:05.840
<font color="lime">But I'm on the way out.</font>

06:05.840 --> 06:07.960
<font color="white">You are no nearer dying than I am.</font>

06:07.960 --> 06:10.200
<font color="white">Now, I want you to take this,</font>
<font color="white">and fill it up.</font>

06:11.720 --> 06:13.920
<font color="white">For pity's sake,</font>
<font color="white">don't let that blanket slip.</font>

06:17.040 --> 06:19.800
<font color="lime">Oh! Pick it up. Come on, woman!</font>

06:24.800 --> 06:29.080
<font color="cyan">Sylvie Bailey, I have told you</font>
<font color="cyan">to lay off my fags. </font><font color="white">Ow!</font>

06:29.080 --> 06:30.640
<font color="cyan">Now sit down.</font>

06:36.000 --> 06:38.440
<font color="cyan">They say girls are easier,</font>
<font color="cyan">but you try me</font>

06:38.440 --> 06:40.160
<font color="cyan">more than your brothers ever did.</font>

06:51.880 --> 06:54.320
<font color="cyan">That coloured woman</font>
<font color="cyan">bothering you again, Sylvie?</font>

06:57.360 --> 06:58.880
<font color="yellow">Mrs Monique Hyde?</font>

07:09.600 --> 07:11.440
<font color="yellow">If you would go through, please.</font>

07:22.600 --> 07:26.360
<font color="cyan">Very high sugar levels, Sister.</font>
<font color="cyan">1.5%.</font>

07:26.360 --> 07:29.040
<font color="white">No more pies. And no more beer.</font>

07:29.040 --> 07:31.560
<font color="white">You've been told to give up pastry,</font>
<font color="white">sugar and potatoes,</font>

07:31.560 --> 07:33.880
<font color="white">but you ignored it.</font>
<font color="white">Now look where we are!</font>

07:33.880 --> 07:35.880
<font color="white">Sky high sugar and injections.</font>

07:35.880 --> 07:39.000
<font color="lime">Injections?</font>
<font color="white">Insulin. Twice a day.</font>

07:39.000 --> 07:41.720
<font color="lime">No, no, no, no. You don't take</font>
<font color="lime">old John down that way.</font>

07:41.720 --> 07:44.400
<font color="lime">I'll fight anyone who tries.</font>
<font color="lime">You tell 'er!</font>

07:44.400 --> 07:46.600
<font color="white">He won't take the needle,</font>
<font color="white">Sister. Hates 'em.</font>

07:50.800 --> 07:52.480
<font color="white">HE SHRIEKS</font>

07:54.920 --> 07:57.760
<font color="cyan">You can expect Nurse Miller</font>
<font color="cyan">every day, twice a day.</font>

08:04.280 --> 08:06.880
<font color="yellow">I'd like to give your husband</font>
<font color="yellow">a good talking to.</font>

08:06.880 --> 08:08.960
<font color="yellow">Moving house would be bad enough,</font>

08:08.960 --> 08:13.240
<font color="yellow">moving the other side of the world</font>
<font color="yellow">when you're 35 weeks pregnant!</font>

08:13.240 --> 08:17.040
<font color="white">The world seems much smaller</font>
<font color="white">when you've been in the Air Force.</font>

08:17.040 --> 08:18.000
<font color="yellow">He flew in the war?</font>

08:19.120 --> 08:22.920
<font color="white">And longed to get back to</font>
<font color="white">the mother country ever since.</font>

08:22.920 --> 08:25.360
<font color="white">Made me believe Vera Lynn would</font>
<font color="white">meet me at Dover.</font>

08:27.200 --> 08:28.760
<font color="white">I must have just missed her.</font>

08:28.760 --> 08:31.600
<font color="yellow">If it's any consolation,</font>
<font color="yellow">the Pearly Kings and Queens</font>

08:31.600 --> 08:33.200
<font color="yellow">didn't meet me in Poplar either.</font>

08:34.400 --> 08:36.559
<font color="yellow">Is your husband</font>
<font color="yellow">still in the airforce?</font>

08:36.559 --> 08:39.240
<font color="white">They wouldn't take him</font>
<font color="white">back after the war.</font>

08:39.240 --> 08:42.520
<font color="white">They said his eyesight</font>
<font color="white">was not good enough.</font>

08:42.520 --> 08:45.120
<font color="white">Though my Harold says</font>
<font color="white">it's no different.</font>

08:46.920 --> 08:49.120
<font color="white">He's got a position at the docks.</font>

08:49.120 --> 08:51.320
<font color="white">They're not easy to come by.</font>

08:52.960 --> 08:54.480
<font color="white">We're very lucky.</font>

08:55.960 --> 08:58.720
<font color="yellow">For a home delivery</font>
<font color="yellow">we shall want to see you at home,</font>

08:58.720 --> 09:01.560
<font color="yellow">make sure everything's</font>
<font color="yellow">as it should be for baby.</font>

09:01.560 --> 09:04.920
<font color="white">You're very kind, but I shall come</font>
<font color="white">to you when my time comes.</font>

09:04.920 --> 09:07.600
<font color="yellow">I'd like to see you try.</font>
<font color="yellow">It's our standard procedure.</font>

09:07.600 --> 09:12.680
<font color="cyan">Sylvie Bailey, SIT DOWN.</font>
<font color="cyan">Sit down before I wallop ya!</font>

09:12.680 --> 09:14.960
<font color="white">One thing about my neighbour...</font>

09:16.280 --> 09:19.880
<font color="white">..we always know exactly how</font>
<font color="white">she feels, about everything.</font>

09:19.880 --> 09:23.520
<font color="yellow">Oh, yes, of course,</font>
<font color="yellow">Mrs Bailey lives next door to you.</font>

09:24.920 --> 09:27.080
<font color="yellow">Rumour has it</font>
<font color="yellow">she has a heart of gold.</font>

09:27.080 --> 09:29.920
<font color="yellow">Though we'll probably need</font>
<font color="yellow">a postmortem to prove it.</font>

09:38.720 --> 09:41.720
<font color="lime">When are we going to get</font>
<font color="lime">to take her for a spin?</font>

09:41.720 --> 09:44.040
<font color="cyan">It's not a toy.</font>
<font color="cyan">In the wrong hands, it's a weapon.</font>

09:44.040 --> 09:46.320
<font color="lime">My hairdryer has more power.</font>

09:46.320 --> 09:50.080
<font color="lime">And if they were that dangerous they</font>
<font color="lime">wouldn't let the Italians ride them.</font>

09:50.080 --> 09:52.600
<font color="cyan">Oi, don't knock the Italians -</font>
<font color="cyan">they gave us Sophia Loren.</font>

10:10.760 --> 10:14.320
<font color="lime">Hello, international nun of mystery.</font>

10:14.320 --> 10:17.520
<font color="lime">I've figured it out -</font>
<font color="lime">you're on the run.</font>

10:17.520 --> 10:20.680
<font color="lime">You did a number in Geneva,</font>
<font color="lime">escaped with the proceeds,</font>

10:20.680 --> 10:24.280
<font color="lime">the habit's a disguise, TB -</font>
<font color="lime">pure cover story. Jane Bond.</font>

10:25.480 --> 10:27.400
<font color="lime">Or you have absolutely no curiosity,</font>

10:27.400 --> 10:29.360
<font color="lime">and that's why you never</font>
<font color="lime">open your mail.</font>

10:35.280 --> 10:37.960
<font color="lime">Oh, and if you happen to be</font>
<font color="lime">praying today,</font>

10:37.960 --> 10:39.600
<font color="lime">be a brick and say one for me.</font>

10:39.600 --> 10:42.200
<font color="lime">I put a lethal amount of gin</font>
<font color="lime">away at the weekend</font>

10:42.200 --> 10:45.520
<font color="lime">and behaved badly with a man</font>
<font color="lime">I feel utterly immoral about.</font>

10:45.520 --> 10:49.480
<font color="yellow">There are souls in want of saving</font>
<font color="yellow">quicker than your own, Nurse Peters.</font>

10:49.480 --> 10:50.920
<font color="yellow">Take it from me.</font>

11:00.600 --> 11:04.440
<font color="lime">Swap you my demonstration</font>
<font color="lime">of nappies for one of those?</font>

11:04.440 --> 11:06.440
<font color="white">Oh, no dice, I'm afraid.</font>

11:06.440 --> 11:10.640
<font color="lime">Sister Bernadette used to do this</font>
<font color="lime">in seconds. Takes me forever.</font>

11:10.640 --> 11:13.080
<font color="white">Any news of Sister Bernadette?</font>

11:13.080 --> 11:17.000
<font color="lime">Food's plentiful, conversation fair</font>
<font color="lime">to middling, health much the same.</font>

11:17.000 --> 11:20.400
<font color="lime">She may not be Jane Austen quite yet</font>
<font color="lime">but her letters are regular...</font>

11:20.400 --> 11:23.400
<font color="lime">though lacking in gossip</font>
<font color="lime">of any kind.</font>

11:23.400 --> 11:26.800
<font color="lime">Hopefully I'll get the low-down</font>
<font color="lime">when I visit her tomorrow.</font>

11:26.800 --> 11:29.560
<font color="white">Well, that's all ticketyboo</font>
<font color="white">and marvellous.</font>

11:31.320 --> 11:32.680
<font color="white">Oh, do give her my regards.</font>

11:32.680 --> 11:34.200
<font color="white">CUTLERY CLATTERS</font>

11:39.560 --> 11:41.040
<font color="lime">"Ticketyboo"?</font>

11:44.440 --> 11:47.640
<font color="cyan">Mrs Lacey, tell me</font>
<font color="cyan">that's not a pie for your husband?</font>

11:47.640 --> 11:49.480
<font color="white">It's hard not to do as he wants.</font>

11:49.480 --> 11:50.680
<font color="cyan">He's ill.</font>

11:50.680 --> 11:54.240
<font color="cyan">Controlling his diet is a very large</font>
<font color="cyan">part of managing his condition.</font>

11:54.240 --> 11:56.200
<font color="white">Sorry, Miss. Sorry.</font>

11:56.200 --> 11:58.840
<font color="white">JOHN SHOUTS ANGRILY</font>

11:58.840 --> 12:02.720
<font color="cyan">Doing what he wants isn't</font>
<font color="cyan">the same as doing what's best.</font>

12:02.720 --> 12:05.800
<font color="cyan">You being stronger -</font>
<font color="cyan">it will help him, Mrs Lacey.</font>

12:05.800 --> 12:07.000
<font color="cyan">Do you understand?</font>

12:07.000 --> 12:08.120
<font color="white">JOHN: </font><font color="lime">Come on, woman!</font>

12:10.520 --> 12:12.280
<font color="lime">Where have you put my paper?!</font>

12:14.640 --> 12:18.480
<font color="white">Then it's out the way...</font>
<font color="white">where it can't do no harm.</font>

12:20.200 --> 12:22.280
<font color="white">You take it when you go. </font><font color="cyan">Thank you.</font>

12:32.880 --> 12:35.400
<font color="yellow">Mmmmm... it's delicious.</font>

12:35.400 --> 12:37.800
<font color="lime">And thoroughly</font>
<font color="lime">unforgiving on the hips.</font>

12:37.800 --> 12:40.320
<font color="cyan">Poor Mrs Lacey. She puts all</font>
<font color="cyan">her love into the pies -</font>

12:40.320 --> 12:42.320
<font color="cyan">her husband certainly</font>
<font color="cyan">doesn't want it.</font>

12:42.320 --> 12:43.960
<font color="yellow">He sounds like a beast.</font>

12:43.960 --> 12:46.520
<font color="lime">Thank God you're looking after him,</font>
<font color="lime">Cynthia.</font>

12:46.520 --> 12:49.520
<font color="lime">I think I'd feed him pies</font>
<font color="lime">to help him pop his clogs.</font>

12:49.520 --> 12:52.520
<font color="lime">Like all bullies though, the minute</font>
<font color="lime">you say boo to him he'll crumble.</font>

12:52.520 --> 12:55.640
<font color="cyan">I just wish I could help</font>
<font color="cyan">Mrs Lacey to say boo.</font>

12:55.640 --> 12:57.080
<font color="lime">Boo. </font><font color="yellow">Boo!</font>

12:57.080 --> 12:58.560
<font color="white">LAUGHTER</font>

12:58.560 --> 13:03.000
<font color="lime">There, see? We'll give her lessons.</font>
<font color="lime">No man will ever bully us.</font>

13:08.400 --> 13:10.080
<font color="white">HE MIMICS MOTORBIKE REVVING</font>

13:12.320 --> 13:14.680
<font color="white">What on earth are you doing?</font>

13:14.680 --> 13:15.920
<font color="cyan">Er, I've just, er...</font>

13:17.440 --> 13:20.600
<font color="cyan">..fitted the rack for the gas and</font>
<font color="cyan">air, and I had to check the tyres</font>

13:20.600 --> 13:21.840
<font color="cyan">and the suspension.</font>

13:21.840 --> 13:25.120
<font color="cyan">These things are a death trap really</font>
<font color="cyan">if they're not maintained properly.</font>

13:25.120 --> 13:27.640
<font color="white">Well, if the Blitz and the Great Smog</font>
<font color="white">didn't polish us off</font>

13:27.640 --> 13:29.200
<font color="white">I think we might survive it.</font>

14:04.120 --> 14:08.680
<font color="cyan">Oh, sorry, sorry, Nurse. Just</font>
<font color="cyan">trying to keep the place sanitary.</font>

14:08.680 --> 14:10.080
<font color="yellow">Good day, Mrs Bailey.</font>

14:15.880 --> 14:18.720
<font color="cyan">Every time a boat comes in</font>
<font color="cyan">there's another one.</font>

14:18.720 --> 14:20.360
<font color="cyan">Six coloureds in there now.</font>

14:27.240 --> 14:29.520
<font color="white">Oh, Miss, it's you.</font>

14:29.520 --> 14:31.120
<font color="yellow">May I come in, Mrs Hyde?</font>

14:31.120 --> 14:34.080
<font color="yellow">We like to make sure everything's</font>
<font color="yellow">in order for a home delivery</font>

14:34.080 --> 14:36.040
<font color="yellow">and I was just passing.</font>

14:36.040 --> 14:38.040
<font color="yellow">It'll only take a moment.</font>

14:43.160 --> 14:45.000
<font color="lime">I can't eat this slop.</font>
<font color="white">SMASHING</font>

14:45.000 --> 14:47.440
<font color="white">John, please!</font>
<font color="lime">Come here, you hag of a woman!</font>

14:47.440 --> 14:49.840
<font color="cyan">You stop this instant.</font>
<font color="lime">Out of my way. </font><font color="cyan">Make me!</font>

14:49.840 --> 14:51.560
<font color="white">Please, Miss, don't worry yourself.</font>

14:51.560 --> 14:54.120
<font color="cyan">You are having "slop"</font>
<font color="cyan">to keep you alive.</font>

14:54.120 --> 14:56.520
<font color="cyan">You are having "slop"</font>
<font color="cyan">on my instructions,</font>

14:56.520 --> 14:59.160
<font color="cyan">so if you want to bully someone,</font>
<font color="cyan">bully me.</font>

14:59.160 --> 15:01.280
<font color="lime">A man can't live on baby food.</font>

15:01.280 --> 15:03.080
<font color="cyan">He can if he behaves like one.</font>

15:06.160 --> 15:08.720
<font color="cyan">Now, I suggest you go</font>
<font color="cyan">and do something useful</font>

15:08.720 --> 15:10.800
<font color="cyan">and provide me with a urine sample.</font>

15:25.800 --> 15:28.280
<font color="cyan">You shouldn't have to put up</font>
<font color="cyan">with this.</font>

15:28.280 --> 15:31.440
<font color="white">I'd better get this up before</font>
<font color="white">someone hurts themselves.</font>

15:58.920 --> 16:01.720
<font color="yellow">Mrs Hyde, I'm afraid I have</font>
<font color="yellow">to ask for our notes -</font>

16:01.720 --> 16:03.600
<font color="yellow">where do you and your husband sleep?</font>

16:03.600 --> 16:07.240
<font color="white">My Harold's cousin and his wife</font>
<font color="white">gave up their own room for us.</font>

16:08.680 --> 16:10.560
<font color="yellow">But there are six of you here?</font>

16:12.720 --> 16:18.440
<font color="white">Mrs Bailey likes to talk. Jacob has</font>
<font color="white">two brothers... we're quiet people.</font>

16:18.440 --> 16:19.920
<font color="white">We get along with it.</font>

16:19.920 --> 16:21.480
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

16:22.640 --> 16:24.680
<font color="white">We intend to take rooms of our own.</font>

16:24.680 --> 16:27.640
<font color="white">It's just not that easy to find them</font>
<font color="white">that will rent to us.</font>

16:29.120 --> 16:31.160
<font color="white">The colour bar, Miss.</font>

16:31.160 --> 16:32.360
<font color="yellow">Oh.</font>

16:36.520 --> 16:38.120
<font color="yellow">My mother has this china.</font>

16:39.320 --> 16:41.720
<font color="white">Mine too. I brought it with me...</font>

16:43.200 --> 16:45.400
<font color="white">..to remind me of her.</font>

16:45.400 --> 16:46.920
<font color="yellow">You must miss her.</font>

16:49.360 --> 16:50.920
<font color="white">Like the sunshine.</font>

16:52.840 --> 16:56.040
<font color="white">And the flowers she used to bring me</font>
<font color="white">from her garden...</font>

16:57.320 --> 16:59.760
<font color="white">..her "English Garden"</font>
<font color="white">is what she called it.</font>

17:01.120 --> 17:03.720
<font color="white">I used to think everyone</font>
<font color="white">in England drank tea</font>

17:03.720 --> 17:06.680
<font color="white">and grew beautiful flowers</font>
<font color="white">in their gardens.</font>

17:15.240 --> 17:17.760
<font color="cyan">You shouldn't be doing all this</font>
<font color="cyan">on your own.</font>

17:17.760 --> 17:19.200
<font color="white">S'all right. I'm strong enough.</font>

17:26.599 --> 17:28.880
<font color="cyan">He shouldn't treat you</font>
<font color="cyan">the way he does.</font>

17:33.760 --> 17:36.800
<font color="white">No treatment's worse than dragging</font>
<font color="white">yourself through the streets,</font>

17:36.800 --> 17:41.520
<font color="white">nowhere to rest your head,</font>
<font color="white">nowhere to rest the baby.</font>

17:41.520 --> 17:43.640
<font color="cyan">You were homeless?</font>

17:43.640 --> 17:46.840
<font color="white">Long time ago, Miss.</font>
<font color="white">Don't pay it no mind.</font>

17:46.840 --> 17:49.720
<font color="white">It showed me what I could</font>
<font color="white">and couldn't stand.</font>

17:51.320 --> 17:55.120
<font color="white">I raised my son, my Bob,</font>
<font color="white">safe and well.</font>

17:55.120 --> 17:58.200
<font color="white">And now that he's grown</font>
<font color="white">I don't need to worry about nothing.</font>

18:04.320 --> 18:05.840
<font color="cyan">Thank you.</font>

18:11.440 --> 18:12.920
<font color="white">JOHN: </font><font color="lime">Woman!</font>

18:17.560 --> 18:19.000
<font color="cyan">He's a bully.</font>

18:19.000 --> 18:22.520
<font color="cyan">He makes his poor wife's life</font>
<font color="cyan">a misery and she puts up with it</font>

18:22.520 --> 18:25.720
<font color="cyan">because she's so pitifully</font>
<font color="cyan">grateful for a roof over her head.</font>

18:25.720 --> 18:27.400
<font color="white">A week of living on the streets,</font>

18:27.400 --> 18:29.360
<font color="white">you'd be surprised</font>
<font color="white">what you'd put up with.</font>

18:29.360 --> 18:31.800
<font color="white">If a wolf had offered her shelter,</font>
<font color="white">she'd have thanked him</font>

18:31.800 --> 18:34.400
<font color="white">for all eternity.</font>
<font color="cyan">She's not on the streets any more -</font>

18:34.400 --> 18:36.000
<font color="cyan">she could stand up to him.</font>

18:37.280 --> 18:39.640
<font color="white">Ain't you been here long enough yet?</font>

18:39.640 --> 18:42.640
<font color="white">We don't have Hollywood endings</font>
<font color="white">here, Nurse Miller.</font>

18:42.640 --> 18:43.720
<font color="white">We just do our jobs.</font>

18:55.080 --> 18:58.240
<font color="lime">I have to say, the tuberculosis</font>
<font color="lime">doctors are extremely</font>

18:58.240 --> 18:59.680
<font color="lime">pleasing on the eye.</font>

18:59.680 --> 19:02.240
<font color="yellow">And extremely well-qualified</font>
<font color="yellow">and good at their jobs.</font>

19:02.240 --> 19:03.360
<font color="lime">What a bonus!</font>

19:03.360 --> 19:06.960
<font color="lime">Oh, I've been dying to know</font>
<font color="lime">what's inside.</font>

19:06.960 --> 19:09.920
<font color="lime">Young Timothy Turner insisted</font>
<font color="lime">I gave it to you personally.</font>

19:09.920 --> 19:11.880
<font color="lime">Oh, and Mrs B</font>
<font color="lime">hopes you enjoy the cake.</font>

19:17.480 --> 19:20.720
<font color="lime">A dead butterfly. Peculiar boy.</font>

19:20.720 --> 19:25.720
<font color="yellow">Pieris brassicae. He wants me to</font>
<font color="yellow">ask the doctors for a diagnosis.</font>

19:27.000 --> 19:28.920
<font color="yellow">Apparently, it's</font>
<font color="yellow">not his father's area.</font>

19:28.920 --> 19:32.440
<font color="lime">I'd say the pin sticking</font>
<font color="lime">through it didn't help.</font>

19:32.440 --> 19:34.200
<font color="yellow">He found him dead on the windowsill.</font>

19:35.520 --> 19:39.120
<font color="yellow">Besides, an enquiring mind</font>
<font color="yellow">is always to be admired.</font>

19:44.040 --> 19:46.640
<font color="yellow">How is... How is everyone?</font>

19:46.640 --> 19:48.280
<font color="lime">We're all perfectly fine.</font>

19:48.280 --> 19:51.080
<font color="lime">But frankly we've had enough</font>
<font color="lime">of this sanitorium business.</font>

19:51.080 --> 19:52.440
<font color="lime">We'd like you to come home.</font>

19:52.440 --> 19:55.440
<font color="lime">With Chummy coming back it will be</font>
<font color="lime">just like old times again.</font>

20:02.000 --> 20:04.640
<font color="white">He's coming home. He's coming home!</font>

20:05.880 --> 20:10.840
<font color="white">My Bob. Home from America!</font>
<font color="white">With his fi-an-ce.</font>

20:10.840 --> 20:13.480
<font color="white">He has a fi-an-ce!</font>

20:13.480 --> 20:18.520
<font color="cyan">Oh, Mrs Lacey, how wonderful.</font>
<font color="cyan">When will he be here?</font>

20:18.520 --> 20:22.320
<font color="white">Why, any day.</font>
<font color="white">And he shall stay three weeks.</font>

20:22.320 --> 20:25.840
<font color="white">Ooh, and look, look at this.</font>
<font color="white">He sent it me.</font>

20:27.240 --> 20:29.760
<font color="white">Says I must have my own</font>
<font color="white">transistor radio.</font>

20:30.880 --> 20:34.120
<font color="white">Says there's a programme I can</font>
<font color="white">listen to every week about America.</font>

20:34.120 --> 20:37.840
<font color="cyan">Oh, yes, Letter From America.</font>
<font color="cyan">Sister Monica Joan adores it.</font>

20:37.840 --> 20:41.080
<font color="white">Says I must listen to it</font>
<font color="white">and think of him. </font><font color="cyan">Ahh.</font>

20:41.080 --> 20:43.080
<font color="white">I can carry it around everywhere.</font>

20:43.080 --> 20:45.200
<font color="white">Don't weigh more than</font>
<font color="white">a bag of sugar.</font>

20:45.200 --> 20:47.600
<font color="white">Ain't got a clue how to switch it on</font>
<font color="white">but that don't matter.</font>

20:47.600 --> 20:49.880
<font color="cyan">You must... you'll love it.</font>

20:49.880 --> 20:52.280
<font color="cyan">Here, I'll show you how it works.</font>

20:54.160 --> 20:55.800
<font color="white">RADIO CRACKLES</font>

20:55.800 --> 20:58.280
<font color="white">MUSIC: "Volare" by Dean Martin</font>

20:58.280 --> 21:00.440
<font color="white"># Oh, oh-oh</font>

21:02.400 --> 21:04.920
<font color="white"># Cantare</font>

21:06.200 --> 21:08.520
<font color="white"># Oh-oh oh-oh</font>

21:10.480 --> 21:13.440
<font color="white"># Let's fly way up to the clouds</font>

21:15.200 --> 21:18.000
<font color="white"># Away from the maddening crowds... #</font>

21:19.800 --> 21:22.560
<font color="lime">He's coming home. He's coming home!</font>

21:22.560 --> 21:26.760
<font color="cyan">Then let's make sure we're as well</font>
<font color="cyan">as we can be for him, shall we?</font>

21:26.760 --> 21:28.560
<font color="lime">I shall need a new razor.</font>

21:28.560 --> 21:32.440
<font color="lime">And some of that stuff that smells</font>
<font color="lime">nice - pomade, that's it.</font>

21:32.440 --> 21:34.720
<font color="lime">And my good suit. Should still fit.</font>

21:34.720 --> 21:38.640
<font color="lime">Tell her, would you, my old lady?</font>
<font color="lime">Tell her what I need.</font>

21:38.640 --> 21:41.040
<font color="cyan">I won't tell her anything, Mr Lacey.</font>

21:41.040 --> 21:43.640
<font color="cyan">I suggest you ask her yourself,</font>
<font color="cyan">nicely.</font>

21:46.800 --> 21:49.840
<font color="white"># Cantare</font>

21:51.280 --> 21:53.040
<font color="white"># Oh-oh oh-oh</font>

21:55.040 --> 21:58.200
<font color="white"># No wonder my happy heart sings</font>

21:58.200 --> 22:01.360
<font color="white"># Your love has given me wings</font>

22:03.360 --> 22:08.600
<font color="white"># Penso che un sogno cosi</font>
<font color="white">non ritorni mai piu</font>

22:10.800 --> 22:14.720
<font color="white"># Mi dipinge con le mani e</font>
<font color="white">la faccia di blu</font>

22:17.200 --> 22:22.080
<font color="white"># Poi d'improvviso venivo</font>
<font color="white">dal vento rapito</font>

22:24.880 --> 22:32.600
<font color="white"># E incominciavo a volare</font>
<font color="white">nel cielo infinito</font>

22:34.440 --> 22:36.160
<font color="white"># Volare... #</font>

22:42.480 --> 22:45.680
<font color="yellow">And... mirror, signal.</font>

22:45.680 --> 22:46.840
<font color="lime">ALL: Mirror, signal.</font>

22:46.840 --> 22:49.960
<font color="white">Oh, I'm so sorry!</font>

22:49.960 --> 22:51.440
<font color="yellow">Imagine the chairs</font>

22:51.440 --> 22:55.280
<font color="yellow">are cars, pedestrians,</font>
<font color="yellow">or other road users.</font>

22:55.280 --> 22:58.920
<font color="white">When do we actually get to</font>
<font color="white">go on the scooter, Fred?</font>

22:58.920 --> 23:02.880
<font color="yellow">When you are proficient and no</font>
<font color="yellow">longer a danger to other road users.</font>

23:02.880 --> 23:05.200
<font color="yellow">Nurse Franklin, mind the chair.</font>

23:05.200 --> 23:09.560
<font color="lime">I've got a run in my stockings.</font>
<font color="lime">Counts as an emergency stop.</font>

23:26.840 --> 23:29.640
<font color="yellow">Sister Monica Joan?</font>
<font color="yellow">You'll catch a chill.</font>

23:31.960 --> 23:35.800
<font color="cyan">Child, were it not for the flowers</font>
<font color="cyan">you carry which imbue you</font>

23:35.800 --> 23:39.800
<font color="cyan">with an air of innocence,</font>
<font color="cyan">I would curse you where you stand.</font>

23:41.200 --> 23:44.360
<font color="cyan">Can you not see the task</font>
<font color="cyan">I am undertaking?</font>

23:46.200 --> 23:48.640
<font color="cyan">Buried beneath us lie the keys.</font>

23:49.840 --> 23:52.520
<font color="cyan">If I have the keys, I can get out.</font>

24:01.280 --> 24:03.440
<font color="cyan">You can come with me.</font>

24:10.000 --> 24:13.840
<font color="yellow">I like it here. You like it here.</font>

24:37.320 --> 24:39.080
<font color="white">He'll be here any minute.</font>

24:39.080 --> 24:40.680
<font color="white">I wanted to be at my best.</font>

24:44.600 --> 24:46.200
<font color="white">It's too bright, ain't it?</font>

24:46.200 --> 24:49.040
<font color="cyan">You could wear Billy Smart's tent</font>

24:49.040 --> 24:51.280
<font color="cyan">and Bob would think you look</font>
<font color="cyan">wonderful.</font>

24:51.280 --> 24:54.080
<font color="lime">Where is he then?</font>
<font color="white">He'll be here. By and by.</font>

24:56.120 --> 24:58.760
<font color="lime">You look like a tin</font>
<font color="lime">of strawberries exploded!</font>

24:58.760 --> 25:00.800
<font color="lime">He'll think we dropped</font>
<font color="lime">the bomb again.</font>

25:00.800 --> 25:02.200
<font color="white">How you do hurt me, John.</font>

25:02.200 --> 25:04.320
<font color="lime">I'm joking, you daft mare.</font>

25:04.320 --> 25:06.680
<font color="cyan">You look lovely, Mrs Lacey.</font>

25:06.680 --> 25:10.480
<font color="white">Well, it is new, and that</font>
<font color="white">counts for something, don't it?</font>

25:30.080 --> 25:31.480
<font color="yellow">It's not just a myth.</font>

25:31.480 --> 25:33.400
<font color="yellow">Some of us do grow flowers</font>
<font color="yellow">and drink tea.</font>

25:35.480 --> 25:36.640
<font color="white">SHE MOANS</font>

25:36.640 --> 25:38.200
<font color="yellow">Mrs Hyde?</font>

25:38.200 --> 25:41.720
<font color="yellow">They're Braxton Hicks contractions,</font>
<font color="yellow">Mrs Hyde.</font>

25:43.360 --> 25:46.760
<font color="yellow">They may feel like labour</font>
<font color="yellow">but they're not the real ones.</font>

25:46.760 --> 25:48.680
<font color="white">But they hurt so bad.</font>

25:48.680 --> 25:51.720
<font color="yellow">You've been having what</font>
<font color="yellow">you thought were contractions</font>

25:51.720 --> 25:54.480
<font color="yellow">alone here and you didn't think</font>
<font color="yellow">to telephone us?</font>

25:54.480 --> 25:57.120
<font color="white">And have my neighbours think</font>
<font color="white">I got my own nurse come running</font>

25:57.120 --> 25:58.480
<font color="white">whenever I sneeze?</font>

25:58.480 --> 25:59.640
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry?</font>

25:59.640 --> 26:02.280
<font color="white">They already think</font>
<font color="white">I get too much for nothing.</font>

26:03.560 --> 26:06.040
<font color="white">You have enough to get on with.</font>

26:06.040 --> 26:08.800
<font color="yellow">All I have to get on with</font>
<font color="yellow">are my patients.</font>

26:08.800 --> 26:12.040
<font color="yellow">And I would come out whatever</font>
<font color="yellow">the time, whatever the weather,</font>

26:12.040 --> 26:13.680
<font color="yellow">for whatever worried any of you.</font>

26:15.360 --> 26:18.000
<font color="yellow">Mrs Hyde, my job is looking</font>
<font color="yellow">after you.</font>

26:21.040 --> 26:23.280
<font color="white">You're the English lady</font>
<font color="white">my mother told me about.</font>

26:25.280 --> 26:29.120
<font color="yellow">Well, then you need to promise me</font>
<font color="yellow">to let me look after you.</font>

26:29.120 --> 26:31.240
<font color="yellow">So I can keep the side up</font>
<font color="yellow">for your mother.</font>

26:33.400 --> 26:36.920
<font color="yellow">For goodness' sake,</font>
<font color="yellow">we're only around the corner.</font>

26:51.840 --> 26:55.080
<font color="lime">Highway Code.</font>
<font color="lime">I thought we'd spend tomorrow on it.</font>

26:55.080 --> 26:57.440
<font color="white">Still be on chairs, will they?</font>
<font color="white">More theory?</font>

26:57.440 --> 26:59.720
<font color="yellow">Without the theory, we are dust.</font>

27:02.160 --> 27:03.720
<font color="white">You can't ride one, can you?</font>

27:05.080 --> 27:06.920
<font color="yellow">I beg your pardon?</font>

27:06.920 --> 27:10.240
<font color="white">Tomorrow. By the bike shed.</font>
<font color="white">8am sharp.</font>

27:16.800 --> 27:20.720
<font color="cyan">Miss, I want a word with you.</font>
<font color="cyan">We've been talking.</font>

27:20.720 --> 27:22.120
<font color="yellow">Oh? Who's "we"?</font>

27:22.120 --> 27:25.760
<font color="cyan">Me and the other girls.</font>
<font color="cyan">We want you to come to us first.</font>

27:25.760 --> 27:27.320
<font color="cyan">When you come round here.</font>

27:27.320 --> 27:28.720
<font color="yellow">I don't quite follow.</font>

27:28.720 --> 27:30.800
<font color="cyan">When you do your home visits.</font>

27:30.800 --> 27:32.480
<font color="yellow">And when you say "first"..?</font>

27:32.480 --> 27:35.440
<font color="cyan">Before what's-her-face.</font>
<font color="cyan">The coloured girl.</font>

27:37.360 --> 27:38.400
<font color="yellow">And why's that?</font>

27:38.400 --> 27:40.080
<font color="cyan">Well, we're vulnerable, ain't we?</font>

27:40.080 --> 27:42.360
<font color="cyan">At this late stage,</font>
<font color="cyan">we could go down with all sorts.</font>

27:42.360 --> 27:44.400
<font color="cyan">And you know what</font>
<font color="cyan">they bring in with them,</font>

27:44.400 --> 27:46.120
<font color="cyan">and it ain't just banana spiders.</font>

27:46.120 --> 27:48.240
<font color="cyan">So, it's just ignorant</font>
<font color="cyan">not to mention it.</font>

27:49.520 --> 27:53.440
<font color="yellow">I'll come to you first, Mrs Bailey.</font>
<font color="cyan">See, I knew you'd understand.</font>

27:53.440 --> 27:56.920
<font color="yellow">Because then at the end of my round</font>
<font color="yellow">I'll be able to sit with Mrs Hyde</font>

27:56.920 --> 28:00.240
<font color="yellow">and have a conversation with an</font>
<font color="yellow">intelligent, well-mannered woman.</font>

28:00.240 --> 28:01.600
<font color="yellow">A proper conversation -</font>

28:01.600 --> 28:03.800
<font color="yellow">one that isn't full</font>
<font color="yellow">of narrow-minded judgement.</font>

28:03.800 --> 28:05.720
<font color="yellow">It will help me</font>
<font color="yellow">get through my other visits.</font>

28:12.520 --> 28:14.440
<font color="lime">Fine son you got.</font>

28:17.120 --> 28:20.440
<font color="white">He must just be delayed</font>
<font color="white">or caught up with something.</font>

28:25.440 --> 28:28.520
<font color="white">Oh, no.</font>

28:28.520 --> 28:30.720
<font color="lime">What difference does it make?</font>

28:30.720 --> 28:32.840
<font color="lime">Ain't no-one here to see ya.</font>

28:32.840 --> 28:36.280
<font color="white">No difference. None. There!</font>
<font color="white">Are you happy now?</font>

29:29.640 --> 29:31.200
<font color="yellow">Are you sad, Dad?</font>

29:32.480 --> 29:35.040
<font color="white">How could I be sad</font>
<font color="white">when I've got you?</font>

29:38.000 --> 29:41.760
<font color="yellow">Granny Parker said you used to just</font>
<font color="yellow">sit in the car after Mummy died,</font>

29:41.760 --> 29:44.480
<font color="yellow">like a sheepdog without his sheep.</font>

29:45.680 --> 29:49.200
<font color="white">Did she? How about some fried bread?</font>

29:49.200 --> 29:51.640
<font color="yellow">Yeah. </font><font color="white">Come on, then.</font>

30:19.200 --> 30:21.840
<font color="white">It's all about weight distribution</font>
<font color="white">and speed.</font>

30:21.840 --> 30:27.000
<font color="white">Too slow and it'll collapse on you,</font>
<font color="white">dump you like a sack of spuds.</font>

30:27.000 --> 30:30.200
<font color="white">Too fast and you fly over the top</font>
<font color="white">like a human cannon ball.</font>

30:33.480 --> 30:35.400
<font color="cyan">Ooh... ooh... ooh...</font>

30:37.560 --> 30:40.480
<font color="cyan">If anyone was</font>
<font color="cyan">to see us in this position...</font>

30:40.480 --> 30:42.280
<font color="cyan">with me behind you...</font>

30:42.280 --> 30:44.040
<font color="white">I beg your pardon!</font>

30:44.040 --> 30:46.840
<font color="cyan">I mean, er,</font>
<font color="cyan">with me as your pillion,</font>

30:46.840 --> 30:49.880
<font color="cyan">might we phrase it such that I was</font>
<font color="cyan">demonstrating the machine to you?</font>

30:49.880 --> 30:55.080
<font color="white">We might indeed phrase it that way,</font>
<font color="white">Frederick. We might indeed.</font>

30:58.640 --> 31:02.400
<font color="cyan">Not too fast, not too fast!</font>
<font color="cyan">You don't know the machine!</font>

31:02.400 --> 31:03.360
<font color="white">Know it?</font>

31:03.360 --> 31:06.760
<font color="white">I rode a machine ten times this size</font>
<font color="white">day in, day out during the war.</font>

31:06.760 --> 31:09.600
<font color="white">And I tell you what - I've missed it!</font>

31:13.400 --> 31:15.720
<font color="white">HE WHIMPERS</font>

31:25.680 --> 31:28.200
<font color="lime">You said your parents</font>
<font color="lime">were in hospitality.</font>

31:28.200 --> 31:31.000
<font color="yellow">Pie and mash...</font>
<font color="yellow">it's quite the thing in London.</font>

31:33.200 --> 31:37.720
<font color="lime">We have a room at the Grosvenor.</font>
<font color="lime">I want to enjoy it.</font>

31:37.720 --> 31:40.920
<font color="lime">Show me England, the real England.</font>

31:40.920 --> 31:43.000
<font color="yellow">We can't just go.</font>

31:43.000 --> 31:44.880
<font color="lime">Bob, there's nobody here.</font>

31:46.440 --> 31:50.760
<font color="cyan">Bob? I knew it was you.</font>
<font color="cyan">We were expecting you yesterday.</font>

31:50.760 --> 31:53.840
<font color="cyan">Your mother's talked</font>
<font color="cyan">so much about you.</font>

31:53.840 --> 31:54.920
<font color="lime">Bob.</font>

31:54.920 --> 31:58.800
<font color="cyan">You're not leaving? Your mother's</font>
<font color="cyan">only popped out to pay the rent -</font>

31:58.800 --> 32:00.560
<font color="cyan">she'll be back any minute.</font>

32:00.560 --> 32:03.160
<font color="yellow">Beg your pardon, Miss, but it's</font>
<font color="yellow">just that we've, um... We've...</font>

32:03.160 --> 32:05.840
<font color="lime">I have an appointment</font>
<font color="lime">that I overlooked.</font>

32:05.840 --> 32:08.360
<font color="cyan">Mr Lacey, you can't possibly leave,</font>

32:08.360 --> 32:10.560
<font color="cyan">your mother's living for this.</font>

32:18.400 --> 32:20.920
<font color="white">I knew you'd come. </font><font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

32:30.560 --> 32:33.840
<font color="lime">Well, well, if it ain't the one</font>
<font color="lime">that got away.</font>

32:36.720 --> 32:37.960
<font color="lime">Nurse.</font>

32:37.960 --> 32:39.360
<font color="cyan">Mr Lacey?</font>

32:39.360 --> 32:40.920
<font color="cyan">Let's sit you down.</font>

32:47.400 --> 32:48.760
<font color="lime">I've come to the conclusion</font>

32:48.760 --> 32:52.200
<font color="lime">he's either the dullest man</font>
<font color="lime">on earth or the most exciting one.</font>

32:54.000 --> 32:56.160
<font color="lime">Perhaps we should just</font>
<font color="lime">return to sender?</font>

32:56.160 --> 32:58.080
<font color="lime">Save the poor man his postage.</font>

32:59.400 --> 33:00.840
<font color="lime">Unrewardingly normal.</font>

33:02.160 --> 33:04.960
<font color="yellow">I think I'd like to</font>
<font color="yellow">arrange for a visitor.</font>

33:05.880 --> 33:07.280
<font color="yellow">May I use the telephone?</font>

33:07.280 --> 33:09.040
<font color="lime">I'll dial the number myself.</font>

33:19.000 --> 33:22.440
<font color="cyan">Just got up a little too quickly.</font>
<font color="cyan">Let's get you some water.</font>

33:24.120 --> 33:27.120
<font color="lime">They lie to ya...</font>
<font color="lime">try to keep your spirits up.</font>

33:28.440 --> 33:32.160
<font color="lime">Diabetes. I got my own nurse,</font>
<font color="lime">that's how bad I am.</font>

33:32.160 --> 33:34.120
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry to hear that.</font>

33:34.120 --> 33:36.120
<font color="lime">Why you talking all posh?</font>

33:36.120 --> 33:39.400
<font color="white">He's talking like a gentleman.</font>
<font color="white">I could listen to you all day.</font>

33:40.960 --> 33:43.680
<font color="white">David Niven,</font>
<font color="white">that's who you remind me of.</font>

33:43.680 --> 33:45.600
<font color="yellow">Perhaps the David Niven</font>
<font color="yellow">of insurance, Mum.</font>

33:45.600 --> 33:46.920
<font color="white">SHE LAUGHS</font>

33:49.040 --> 33:52.360
<font color="white">To be married!</font>
<font color="white">My Lord, I dreamed of this.</font>

33:53.640 --> 33:55.280
<font color="white">When are you thinking?</font>

33:55.280 --> 33:57.600
<font color="white">Um, we could get</font>
<font color="white">the Parish Hall, I reckon.</font>

33:59.760 --> 34:02.560
<font color="cyan">We wouldn't want to put you</font>
<font color="cyan">to any trouble.</font>

34:02.560 --> 34:04.320
<font color="cyan">We'll be getting married back home.</font>

34:05.760 --> 34:07.320
<font color="lime">But this is your home.</font>

34:08.520 --> 34:10.520
<font color="yellow">Trudie's parents...</font>
<font color="yellow">they very kindly...</font>

34:10.520 --> 34:13.639
<font color="lime">They have a beautiful house</font>
<font color="lime">overlooking the Hudson River.</font>

34:13.639 --> 34:15.639
<font color="lime">It will be the perfect place.</font>

34:15.639 --> 34:17.840
<font color="white">Hudson River.</font>

34:19.840 --> 34:21.920
<font color="lime">My mother wouldn't forgive us.</font>

34:23.360 --> 34:25.719
<font color="white">Righto, righto, course.</font>

34:25.719 --> 34:26.960
<font color="yellow">We'd like you to be there.</font>

34:26.960 --> 34:32.440
<font color="white">Oh, John. What do you think to that?</font>
<font color="white">Well, it... It could be a holiday.</font>

34:32.440 --> 34:36.760
<font color="lime">No, couldn't travel,</font>
<font color="lime">not with my health.</font>

34:38.199 --> 34:40.600
<font color="lime">You'll have to write,</font>
<font color="lime">tell us how it went.</font>

34:46.520 --> 34:49.199
<font color="cyan">We should probably be going.</font>
<font color="white">You're not stopping?</font>

34:49.199 --> 34:53.000
<font color="cyan">Oh, no,</font>
<font color="cyan">we couldn't put you to the bother.</font>

34:53.000 --> 34:56.000
<font color="white">Wait one minute, won't you,</font>
<font color="white">dear, just a minute?</font>

34:57.640 --> 35:01.560
<font color="cyan">I have another call to make,</font>
<font color="cyan">Mrs Lacey, unless you need me here?</font>

35:01.560 --> 35:03.640
<font color="white">Oh, no, Miss. You go on now.</font>

35:04.880 --> 35:09.080
<font color="white">What a day this has been, Miss.</font>
<font color="white">I've dreamed of a day like today.</font>

35:22.320 --> 35:23.560
<font color="white">SHE SCREAMS</font>

35:24.800 --> 35:28.120
<font color="cyan">Bloody hell! You saved us.</font>

35:43.000 --> 35:44.280
<font color="cyan">Ta.</font>

35:45.880 --> 35:48.240
<font color="white">You'd have done the same for me.</font>

35:50.400 --> 35:54.640
<font color="cyan">Council promise to wash these steps</font>
<font color="cyan">every month. Lying sods.</font>

35:56.280 --> 35:58.520
<font color="white">Then we must look after each other,</font>
<font color="white">Mrs Bailey.</font>

35:58.520 --> 36:00.240
<font color="cyan">How d'you mean?</font>

36:00.240 --> 36:03.280
<font color="white">Where I come from,</font>
<font color="white">we take it in turns...</font>

36:03.280 --> 36:05.080
<font color="white">some of the ladies.</font>

36:06.600 --> 36:10.800
<font color="white">One week I'd scrub the verandas,</font>
<font color="white">next week someone else.</font>

36:12.840 --> 36:14.440
<font color="white">We could do that here.</font>

36:14.440 --> 36:18.560
<font color="cyan">"Verandas". Makes me</font>
<font color="cyan">think of Gone With The Wind.</font>

36:18.560 --> 36:19.560
<font color="cyan">I don't know why.</font>

36:21.880 --> 36:23.640
<font color="cyan">Gawd, I love a bit of Clark Gable.</font>

36:25.520 --> 36:28.240
<font color="white">My mother keeps his picture</font>
<font color="white">beside her bed.</font>

36:28.240 --> 36:29.800
<font color="cyan">I'd do the same.</font>

36:29.800 --> 36:32.480
<font color="cyan">Better than looking at my old man</font>
<font color="cyan">next to me on the pillow.</font>

36:37.640 --> 36:39.800
<font color="cyan">What's it like?</font>

36:41.320 --> 36:42.840
<font color="cyan">Where you come from?</font>

36:45.200 --> 36:53.080
<font color="white">Green. Very green.</font>
<font color="white">And the sea... like jade.</font>

36:54.320 --> 36:56.120
<font color="white">If you climb up high enough,</font>

36:56.120 --> 36:57.760
<font color="white">you can see the whole island.</font>

37:00.360 --> 37:01.920
<font color="white">WOMEN CHATTER</font>

37:03.120 --> 37:05.560
<font color="cyan">Well, I'll have to</font>
<font color="cyan">do my wash again now.</font>

37:05.560 --> 37:06.840
<font color="cyan">All sorts over it.</font>

37:17.680 --> 37:21.760
<font color="lime">It's quaint.</font>
<font color="lime">It's like stepping back in time.</font>

37:21.760 --> 37:25.000
<font color="lime">Yes, that's what it is -</font>
<font color="lime">it's Dickens.</font>

37:26.480 --> 37:30.640
<font color="lime">Oh! </font><font color="white">It were Bob's.</font>
<font color="white">I kept it all these years,</font>

37:30.640 --> 37:32.960
<font color="white">hoping one day there'd be a</font>
<font color="white">reason for it again.</font>

37:35.320 --> 37:36.720
<font color="white">It's yours now, dear.</font>

37:41.480 --> 37:43.480
<font color="lime">Yes, it's very special.</font>

37:49.640 --> 37:51.280
<font color="yellow">Come and see me, Mum.</font>

37:52.800 --> 37:55.200
<font color="yellow">This is my number -</font>
<font color="yellow">at the hotel.</font>

38:07.400 --> 38:10.120
<font color="white">RADIO TUNES IN</font>

38:10.120 --> 38:13.440
<font color="white">SENTIMENTAL MUSIC</font>

38:15.920 --> 38:18.680
<font color="lime">Bob, what do you want me to say?</font>

38:18.680 --> 38:21.160
<font color="lime">I mean, the place was a hole,</font>
<font color="lime">and those people...</font>

38:21.160 --> 38:24.720
<font color="yellow">"Those people"? She's my mother.</font>

38:45.080 --> 38:50.120
<font color="white">Oh! </font><font color="lime">Left it, forgot it,</font>
<font color="lime">don't make no difference.</font>

38:50.120 --> 38:53.040
<font color="white">Well, they can't be that far -</font>
<font color="white">I'll go after her.</font>

38:53.040 --> 38:55.680
<font color="lime">She's got no more interest in this</font>
<font color="lime">than you have in the moon.</font>

38:55.680 --> 38:58.800
<font color="lime">He's found a right harsh one there.</font>
<font color="white">We don't know her yet, John.</font>

38:58.800 --> 39:02.120
<font color="lime">Won't get the chance neither.</font>
<font color="lime">She's in charge, no doubt about it.</font>

39:02.120 --> 39:06.480
<font color="lime">He's marrying up, and she won't</font>
<font color="lime">let him forget that in a hurry.</font>

39:06.480 --> 39:08.560
<font color="lime">Hudson bloody River.</font>

39:08.560 --> 39:10.920
<font color="white">He ain't like that.</font>
<font color="white">He won't be changed.</font>

39:10.920 --> 39:13.960
<font color="lime">Don't see him coming back</font>
<font color="lime">for this, do you?</font>

39:13.960 --> 39:18.520
<font color="white">He's my son.</font>
<font color="white">I know what kind of a man he is!</font>

39:18.520 --> 39:20.200
<font color="lime">He's hers now.</font>

39:23.840 --> 39:29.480
<font color="white"># Can I adore you... #</font>

39:29.480 --> 39:31.480
<font color="white">Good night, Mrs Wilson.</font>
<font color="cyan">See you tomorrow.</font>

39:31.480 --> 39:34.040
<font color="white"># ..Although we are oceans apart</font>

39:35.760 --> 39:40.440
<font color="white"># I can't make you open your heart</font>

39:40.440 --> 39:45.440
<font color="white"># But I can grieve, can't I? #</font>

39:56.560 --> 39:58.280
<font color="lime">Your visitor's here.</font>

40:03.080 --> 40:06.080
<font color="white">Dear Sister. How we have missed you.</font>

40:07.280 --> 40:09.080
<font color="white">God is very kind to us.</font>

40:09.080 --> 40:11.040
<font color="yellow">He is, isn't he?</font>

40:13.800 --> 40:17.440
<font color="yellow">How is life at Nonnatus?</font>
<font color="yellow">I hear Chummy is on her way back.</font>

40:19.000 --> 40:23.200
<font color="lime">Sister, from our letters</font>
<font color="lime">and our visits, you probably know</font>

40:23.200 --> 40:25.800
<font color="lime">more about life at Nonnatus House</font>
<font color="lime">than I do.</font>

40:27.560 --> 40:31.240
<font color="lime">So, please, what is it you can</font>
<font color="lime">say to me now that</font>

40:31.240 --> 40:33.360
<font color="lime">you couldn't say in a letter?</font>

40:36.840 --> 40:40.560
<font color="yellow">I've been lying, Sister.</font>

40:40.560 --> 40:45.200
<font color="yellow">Lying to you, to God, to myself.</font>

40:47.200 --> 40:50.800
<font color="yellow">And I'm so tired. I'm so tired.</font>

40:52.520 --> 40:56.000
<font color="lime">And now you must unburden yourself</font>
<font color="lime">and I will listen.</font>

40:58.240 --> 41:00.280
<font color="white">TALKING ON RADIO</font>

41:00.280 --> 41:03.880
<font color="cyan">I thought Mrs Lacey</font>
<font color="cyan">was enjoying her radio.</font>

41:03.880 --> 41:06.240
<font color="lime">My shop. My wireless.</font>

41:07.840 --> 41:10.680
<font color="cyan">Would you mind turning</font>
<font color="cyan">it down, please?</font>

41:10.680 --> 41:15.000
<font color="cyan">You are perfectly able to travel,</font>
<font color="cyan">you know that. </font><font color="lime">So what if I do?</font>

41:15.000 --> 41:17.640
<font color="cyan">Don't you want to</font>
<font color="cyan">see your son get married?</font>

41:17.640 --> 41:19.320
<font color="lime">He ain't my son.</font>

41:19.320 --> 41:23.760
<font color="lime">I just took him in, put a roof</font>
<font color="lime">over his head, same as I did her.</font>

41:25.400 --> 41:27.400
<font color="cyan">Sorry, I had no idea.</font>

41:27.400 --> 41:30.000
<font color="lime">Ain't so high and mighty now,</font>
<font color="lime">are ya?</font>

41:30.000 --> 41:33.400
<font color="cyan">But don't you think it would mean</font>
<font color="cyan">such an awful lot to Mrs Lacey?</font>

41:33.400 --> 41:36.160
<font color="lime">She and that boy would have</font>
<font color="lime">been in a work house without me.</font>

41:36.160 --> 41:38.360
<font color="white">And I might as well have been.</font>

41:38.360 --> 41:41.080
<font color="lime">You got a nerve.</font>
<font color="lime">I picked you up off the streets.</font>

41:41.080 --> 41:42.480
<font color="lime">I saved you.</font>

41:42.480 --> 41:45.040
<font color="white">And haven't I thanked you</font>
<font color="white">every day for it?</font>

41:46.200 --> 41:49.200
<font color="white">I'm grateful, John,</font>
<font color="white">grateful for everything,</font>

41:49.200 --> 41:51.880
<font color="white">but I've given far more</font>
<font color="white">than I've taken.</font>

41:51.880 --> 41:55.640
<font color="white">I've cared and done for you every</font>
<font color="white">day that we've been together.</font>

41:55.640 --> 41:58.160
<font color="white">And though you might not think</font>
<font color="white">it worth the mention,</font>

41:58.160 --> 41:59.680
<font color="white">I've given you all that I have.</font>

41:59.680 --> 42:01.160
<font color="white">HE SCOFFS</font>

42:10.440 --> 42:13.640
<font color="lime">So all this time you felt unable</font>
<font color="lime">to share your suffering.</font>

42:13.640 --> 42:15.200
<font color="yellow">I thought I'd lost my faith.</font>

42:16.320 --> 42:18.800
<font color="yellow">I never felt so wretched</font>
<font color="yellow">or alone in my life.</font>

42:19.920 --> 42:24.040
<font color="lime">I've been so worried.</font>
<font color="lime">I hoped you would speak to me again.</font>

42:24.040 --> 42:25.720
<font color="yellow">I haven't lost my faith.</font>

42:29.400 --> 42:30.720
<font color="yellow">I want other things.</font>

42:32.360 --> 42:34.800
<font color="yellow">Things I can't have</font>
<font color="yellow">in the religious life.</font>

42:37.320 --> 42:41.320
<font color="lime">We've all felt that -</font>
<font color="lime">times of confusion.</font>

42:42.960 --> 42:44.240
<font color="lime">There were for me.</font>

42:45.600 --> 42:50.080
<font color="yellow">This was my wilderness, my test</font>
<font color="yellow">of what I felt, what I believed.</font>

42:51.480 --> 42:54.400
<font color="yellow">And I see now that</font>
<font color="yellow">I wasn't close to death,</font>

42:54.400 --> 42:57.920
<font color="yellow">I was close to life - and it took</font>
<font color="yellow">the illness to show me.</font>

43:01.920 --> 43:08.000
<font color="yellow">I think God wants another path</font>
<font color="yellow">for me... beyond Nonnatus.</font>

43:12.840 --> 43:18.800
<font color="lime">Sister... what you're saying,</font>
<font color="lime">what you're asking...</font>

43:21.200 --> 43:25.560
<font color="lime">..is the first step on a journey</font>
<font color="lime">which will not be an easy one.</font>

43:27.240 --> 43:29.960
<font color="lime">You must be sure that it is one</font>
<font color="lime">you wish to pursue.</font>

43:31.520 --> 43:33.240
<font color="yellow">I need your strength, Sister.</font>

43:34.760 --> 43:38.040
<font color="yellow">I don't have enough of my own</font>
<font color="yellow">because I don't know if God's given</font>

43:38.040 --> 43:41.960
<font color="yellow">me a window and I'm just staring out</font>
<font color="yellow">of it because I'm afraid to open it?</font>

44:12.080 --> 44:14.680
<font color="white">So I'm going out now.</font>
<font color="white">And I can't says when I'll be back.</font>

44:14.680 --> 44:18.880
<font color="lime">What do you mean, "going out"?</font>
<font color="lime">Where? </font><font color="white">That's my business.</font>

44:18.880 --> 44:21.080
<font color="lime">Where would you be going all</font>
<font color="lime">painted up like that?</font>

44:21.080 --> 44:23.520
<font color="white">I had a life before you, John.</font>

44:23.520 --> 44:26.560
<font color="white">It's about time I found it again.</font>

44:26.560 --> 44:28.320
<font color="cyan">(Well done, Annie!)</font>

44:28.320 --> 44:29.520
<font color="white">Thank you, dear.</font>

44:37.880 --> 44:40.920
<font color="yellow">It's all about weight distribution</font>
<font color="yellow">and speed.</font>

44:40.920 --> 44:42.920
<font color="yellow">Too slow and</font>
<font color="yellow">it will collapse under you,</font>

44:42.920 --> 44:44.560
<font color="yellow">dumping you like a sack of spuds.</font>

44:44.560 --> 44:48.440
<font color="white">Too fast and you'll fly over</font>
<font color="white">the top like a human cannon ball.</font>

44:48.440 --> 44:49.720
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Sister.</font>

44:56.880 --> 44:59.080
<font color="yellow">Don't be afraid of it. Fear kills.</font>

44:59.080 --> 45:00.240
<font color="lime">I'm not.</font>

45:15.320 --> 45:17.520
<font color="lime">A girl with spatial awareness?</font>

45:17.520 --> 45:20.200
<font color="lime">If I had a brain I'd be lethal!</font>

45:22.920 --> 45:24.960
<font color="cyan">One can't turn</font>
<font color="cyan">one's back for a moment.</font>

45:24.960 --> 45:29.480
<font color="cyan">Whatever next - nuns on skis?</font>
<font color="yellow">Chummy! </font><font color="white">Chummy!</font>

45:31.840 --> 45:34.360
<font color="cyan">Make safe the vehicle and step away.</font>

45:34.360 --> 45:36.080
<font color="lime">My hero, as always.</font>

45:36.080 --> 45:38.760
<font color="cyan">Gently, chaps.</font>
<font color="cyan">I've come back a bit top heavy.</font>

45:38.760 --> 45:41.440
<font color="yellow">Oh, Chummy. How wonderful!</font>

45:41.440 --> 45:44.840
<font color="cyan">It is rather, isn't it? It's</font>
<font color="cyan">our little bit of extra luggage.</font>

45:44.840 --> 45:47.240
<font color="yellow">Hello. </font><font color="cyan">Fred.</font>

45:47.240 --> 45:48.560
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

46:00.160 --> 46:01.560
<font color="cyan">Madam. </font><font color="white">Thank you.</font>

46:11.920 --> 46:14.680
<font color="yellow">Mum. </font><font color="white">Hello, love.</font>

46:14.680 --> 46:16.280
<font color="yellow">I'm so glad you came.</font>

46:30.520 --> 46:32.600
<font color="white">I don't want to lose you, Bob.</font>

46:32.600 --> 46:33.800
<font color="yellow">Mum...</font>

46:33.800 --> 46:37.160
<font color="white">That don't mean I expect to be</font>
<font color="white">pride of place - I don't.</font>

46:37.160 --> 46:40.000
<font color="white">You got your life and</font>
<font color="white">I couldn't be more proud of you.</font>

46:41.720 --> 46:44.160
<font color="white">Just make sure you keep it yours.</font>

46:45.320 --> 46:47.600
<font color="white">Live your life the way you want.</font>

46:47.600 --> 46:49.040
<font color="yellow">Like you?</font>

46:49.040 --> 46:55.000
<font color="white">Nothing's perfect. But we keep on,</font>
<font color="white">cos we remember the good bits.</font>

46:57.080 --> 47:00.400
<font color="yellow">Then we must have a long,</font>
<font color="yellow">long lunch, where we remember all</font>

47:00.400 --> 47:04.200
<font color="yellow">those good bits and tell each other</font>
<font color="yellow">all the little things we've missed.</font>

47:04.200 --> 47:06.800
<font color="yellow">Is that all right?</font>
<font color="white">Yes, love, quite all right.</font>

47:08.960 --> 47:10.680
<font color="white">Today I'm on holiday.</font>

47:16.080 --> 47:18.320
<font color="white">Ah, thank you. It's lovely!</font>

47:18.320 --> 47:21.320
<font color="cyan">Now we have some more trinkets</font>
<font color="cyan">from our travels. </font><font color="lime">Ooh. Peter.</font>

47:21.320 --> 47:25.560
<font color="yellow">Sister Monica Joan, I know you</font>
<font color="yellow">have a fondness for percussion.</font>

47:32.880 --> 47:35.360
<font color="cyan">Oh, I shall beat a path</font>
<font color="cyan">to my room...</font>

47:39.080 --> 47:43.280
<font color="cyan">..and send out a warning to all</font>
<font color="cyan">around, "Beware the future -</font>

47:43.280 --> 47:45.200
<font color="cyan">"it is not to be trusted."</font>

47:47.960 --> 47:49.840
<font color="cyan">Great changes are coming.</font>

47:53.200 --> 47:54.920
<font color="yellow">Yes, well, jolly good.</font>

47:54.920 --> 47:56.920
<font color="lime">She does get very tired.</font>
<font color="white">Don't we all?</font>

47:58.120 --> 48:01.680
<font color="yellow">Now, girls, I can't promise</font>
<font color="yellow">this season's colours,</font>

48:01.680 --> 48:04.880
<font color="yellow">but I can promise,</font>
<font color="yellow">with the help of my trusty Singer,</font>

48:04.880 --> 48:07.400
<font color="yellow">no-one else in Poplar will look</font>
<font color="yellow">quite so spiffing.</font>

48:07.400 --> 48:09.000
<font color="cyan">Thank you.</font>

48:11.520 --> 48:15.320
<font color="yellow">And Jane, I went on the letters</font>
<font color="yellow">of Reverend Applebee-Thornton,</font>

48:15.320 --> 48:18.920
<font color="yellow">who assured me that this</font>
<font color="yellow">would be your colour.</font>

48:18.920 --> 48:21.000
<font color="white">It's for me? </font><font color="cyan">Of course for you.</font>

48:21.000 --> 48:24.120
<font color="cyan">From what I hear, we couldn't have</font>
<font color="cyan">managed without you. </font><font color="white">Thank you.</font>

48:24.120 --> 48:27.120
<font color="yellow">Oh, Chummy, they're beautiful.</font>

48:27.120 --> 48:29.960
<font color="cyan">I feel ever so exotic.</font>

48:29.960 --> 48:31.280
<font color="lime">The Belles of Bow!</font>

48:33.560 --> 48:35.000
<font color="white">Thank you very much, it's beautiful.</font>

48:35.000 --> 48:36.800
<font color="cyan">Good.</font>

48:38.160 --> 48:39.200
<font color="white">MUSIC PLAYS</font>

48:41.720 --> 48:44.600
<font color="white">SQUEALING AND GIGGLING</font>

48:44.600 --> 48:46.160
<font color="lime">Oh, yes!</font>

48:55.680 --> 48:57.800
<font color="white">PHONE RINGS</font>

49:09.560 --> 49:10.760
<font color="cyan">'Nonnatus House.'</font>

49:10.760 --> 49:13.760
<font color="white">Midwife, please,</font>
<font color="white">they've started properly now.</font>

49:13.760 --> 49:15.520
<font color="cyan">Who is this, please?</font>

49:15.520 --> 49:20.360
<font color="white">'Mrs Hyde, Mrs Monique Hyde,</font>
<font color="white">18 Old Rope Street Buildings.</font>

49:20.360 --> 49:23.680
<font color="white">'Nurse Lee told me to call you</font>
<font color="white">when they started to come.</font>

49:24.800 --> 49:27.000
<font color="white">Please come quickly.</font>

49:28.440 --> 49:30.400
<font color="white">I'm on my own.</font>

49:32.000 --> 49:34.200
<font color="white">'Hello? Help me...'</font>

49:34.200 --> 49:37.880
<font color="white">Please! </font><font color="cyan">I'm sorry,</font>
<font color="cyan">I'm afraid we're closed.</font>

49:42.560 --> 49:44.280
<font color="white">SHE GASPS AND SOBS</font>

49:50.200 --> 49:55.720
<font color="white">Please don't come, please, not yet.</font>

50:13.720 --> 50:16.160
<font color="white">Sylvie, is your mama there?</font>

50:17.320 --> 50:18.960
<font color="white">You know when she'll be home?</font>

50:22.000 --> 50:23.960
<font color="yellow">Is it your baby, Miss?</font>

50:42.440 --> 50:45.720
<font color="white">I can't have you here. Please.</font>

50:45.720 --> 50:47.920
<font color="cyan">Sylvie Bailey, get home now.</font>

50:47.920 --> 50:50.640
<font color="yellow">But Mum, the lady!</font>

50:52.120 --> 50:54.080
<font color="yellow">I want to stay with her.</font>

50:54.080 --> 50:56.920
<font color="white">Rita, please.</font>

50:58.040 --> 51:01.480
<font color="cyan">Call the bloody midwife.</font>
<font color="white">They don't answer. </font><font color="cyan">They have to.</font>

51:01.480 --> 51:02.640
<font color="cyan">It's their job!</font>

51:05.200 --> 51:06.720
<font color="white">Go back to your friends, Rita.</font>

51:19.080 --> 51:20.720
<font color="cyan">Sylvie, go home now.</font>

51:20.720 --> 51:24.800
<font color="white">Quickly, Rita,</font>
<font color="white">you don't know what she might have!</font>

51:24.800 --> 51:26.560
<font color="cyan">Oh, sod off!</font>

51:28.880 --> 51:30.800
<font color="cyan">Come on. Easy. Breathe.</font>

51:39.400 --> 51:40.960
<font color="white">It's coming.</font>

51:40.960 --> 51:45.560
<font color="cyan">No, no, no. You can't have it here,</font>
<font color="cyan">it, it ain't sanitary.</font>

51:47.480 --> 51:51.960
<font color="cyan">Hold on, hold on, all right?</font>
<font color="cyan">Yeah? Yeah? Come on.</font>

51:51.960 --> 51:55.720
<font color="cyan">Just a little bit more till</font>
<font color="cyan">we get somewhere safe. All right?</font>

52:02.720 --> 52:03.920
<font color="cyan">All right.</font>

52:08.480 --> 52:11.200
<font color="white">There's nothing here,</font>
<font color="white">just scribbles.</font>

52:11.200 --> 52:13.760
<font color="lime">No-one is angry with you.</font>

52:13.760 --> 52:16.320
<font color="lime">It's just very important</font>
<font color="lime">that you try</font>

52:16.320 --> 52:18.440
<font color="lime">and remember who you were</font>
<font color="lime">speaking to.</font>

52:18.440 --> 52:20.920
<font color="yellow">It could be any one</font>
<font color="yellow">of our patients -</font>

52:20.920 --> 52:23.720
<font color="yellow">we have 50 due to deliver</font>
<font color="yellow">this week alone.</font>

52:23.720 --> 52:27.600
<font color="cyan">Her voice was gentle...</font>

52:27.600 --> 52:30.880
<font color="cyan">like a tender breeze</font>
<font color="cyan">on spring leaves.</font>

52:30.880 --> 52:32.080
<font color="white">Oh, give me strength.</font>

52:33.960 --> 52:35.800
<font color="cyan">My thoughts unravel...</font>

52:38.160 --> 52:40.200
<font color="cyan">..like frayed rope...</font>

52:42.840 --> 52:45.400
<font color="cyan">Old Rope Street!</font>

52:47.120 --> 52:49.240
<font color="yellow">Monique Hyde.</font>

53:02.800 --> 53:04.720
<font color="cyan">Come on! Give me your hand.</font>

53:05.720 --> 53:07.600
<font color="cyan">All right, after me, yeah?</font>

53:09.440 --> 53:11.560
<font color="cyan">That's it, nearly there.</font>

53:11.560 --> 53:14.080
<font color="cyan">One step at a time. Yeah? Yeah?</font>

53:17.480 --> 53:21.520
<font color="white">SHE MOANS</font>
<font color="cyan">Help us. Help us!</font>

53:21.520 --> 53:23.040
<font color="cyan">There's a baby coming!</font>

53:24.600 --> 53:26.720
<font color="yellow">Monique? I'm so, so sorry.</font>

53:29.040 --> 53:30.320
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Rita.</font>

53:30.320 --> 53:31.640
<font color="cyan">Where the hell were you lot,</font>

53:31.640 --> 53:34.120
<font color="cyan">leaving a decent woman</font>
<font color="cyan">in this state?! </font><font color="white">Oh, Lord.</font>

53:34.120 --> 53:37.080
<font color="yellow">Get sheets, Trixie. And hot water.</font>
<font color="lime">I know the drill.</font>

53:37.080 --> 53:38.760
<font color="cyan">We don't have much time.</font>

53:38.760 --> 53:41.760
<font color="yellow">We need to get you inside now.</font>
<font color="yellow">Put your arm around me.</font>

53:41.760 --> 53:43.760
<font color="yellow">One, two, three.</font>

53:43.760 --> 53:45.640
<font color="cyan">Upsy-daisy.</font>

53:45.640 --> 53:46.920
<font color="cyan">Nearly there.</font>

53:56.120 --> 53:58.280
<font color="white">I leave matters</font>
<font color="white">in your capable hands.</font>

53:58.280 --> 54:00.720
<font color="white">I must see to Sister Monica Joan.</font>

54:04.000 --> 54:07.320
<font color="lime">Slowly, slowly. There's a girl.</font>

54:10.840 --> 54:12.160
<font color="yellow">Baby's heartbeat is slow.</font>

54:13.760 --> 54:15.320
<font color="cyan">Forgive me, Lord...</font>

54:18.400 --> 54:23.120
<font color="cyan">..and protect us all from these</font>
<font color="cyan">devils that plague me.</font>

54:30.000 --> 54:31.800
<font color="lime">There are no devils here.</font>

54:33.840 --> 54:36.880
<font color="lime">Your mind gets tired, Sister,</font>
<font color="lime">that is all.</font>

54:36.880 --> 54:40.080
<font color="lime">And when it does,</font>
<font color="lime">we will protect you.</font>

54:40.080 --> 54:44.440
<font color="lime">We will be with you and make sure</font>
<font color="lime">that when you forget, we remember.</font>

54:57.400 --> 54:59.960
<font color="yellow">Keep going, Monique. Good!</font>

54:59.960 --> 55:01.600
<font color="white">Hurts so much.</font>

55:01.600 --> 55:05.120
<font color="cyan">Baby cannot come by himself,</font>
<font color="cyan">and we need him out.</font>

55:05.120 --> 55:06.760
<font color="cyan">You need to push.</font>

55:06.760 --> 55:09.600
<font color="yellow">You need all your strength now,</font>
<font color="yellow">Monique.</font>

55:09.600 --> 55:11.400
<font color="yellow">More than you've ever done before.</font>

55:11.400 --> 55:13.800
<font color="yellow">You need to do it for your baby.</font>
<font color="yellow">All right?</font>

55:18.040 --> 55:20.680
<font color="yellow">Good girl. Keep going,</font>
<font color="yellow">good, really good.</font>

55:25.400 --> 55:28.440
<font color="yellow">That's it! Good girl!</font>

55:32.280 --> 55:37.840
<font color="yellow">There's a knot in the cord. That's</font>
<font color="yellow">why baby's heartbeat was slow.</font>

55:37.840 --> 55:39.320
<font color="white">My baby?</font>

55:39.320 --> 55:42.120
<font color="yellow">..Is absolutely perfect.</font>

55:42.120 --> 55:44.960
<font color="yellow">You have a beautiful baby boy.</font>

55:46.600 --> 55:48.480
<font color="yellow">Welcome to England, little one.</font>

55:59.480 --> 56:04.600
<font color="white">From this whole mother country,</font>
<font color="white">you picked the nicest ladies to</font>

56:04.600 --> 56:06.840
<font color="white">introduce you.</font>

56:09.320 --> 56:10.640
<font color="white">Thank you.</font>

56:14.240 --> 56:16.880
<font color="cyan">Of course, in the bush</font>
<font color="cyan">we would light a fire primarily</font>

56:16.880 --> 56:21.000
<font color="cyan">to ward off lions...</font>
<font color="lime">And tigers. </font><font color="yellow">And bears. </font><font color="white">Oh, my!</font>

56:21.000 --> 56:23.000
<font color="white">THEY LAUGH</font>

56:24.320 --> 56:27.480
<font color="yellow">The whites of a lion's eyes are no</font>
<font color="yellow">laughing matter, I can assure you.</font>

56:27.480 --> 56:30.560
<font color="cyan">Nor is the advancing derriere</font>
<font color="cyan">of an elephant in reverse.</font>

56:30.560 --> 56:32.680
<font color="cyan">A pair of my spectacles is</font>
<font color="cyan">testament to that.</font>

56:32.680 --> 56:34.400
<font color="white">LAUGHTER</font>

56:34.400 --> 56:38.120
<font color="yellow">Won't you miss your wonderful</font>
<font color="yellow">adventures?</font>

56:38.120 --> 56:40.240
<font color="cyan">I think we have more than</font>
<font color="cyan">we could have dreamt of</font>

56:40.240 --> 56:41.720
<font color="cyan">just around the corner.</font>

56:53.440 --> 56:56.120
<font color="white">MATURE JENNY:</font>
<font color="yellow">'Home is not simply a mark</font>

56:56.120 --> 57:00.040
<font color="yellow">'upon a map any more</font>
<font color="yellow">than a river's just water.</font>

57:00.040 --> 57:03.600
<font color="yellow">'It is the place at the centre</font>
<font color="yellow">of the compass</font>

57:03.600 --> 57:09.960
<font color="yellow">'from which every arrow radiates</font>
<font color="yellow">and where the heart is fixed.</font>

57:09.960 --> 57:16.000
<font color="yellow">'It is a force that forever draws</font>
<font color="yellow">us back or lures us on.'</font>

57:21.720 --> 57:23.080
<font color="white">Thank you.</font>

57:30.400 --> 57:32.560
<font color="white">MUSIC PLAYS</font>

57:50.120 --> 57:55.000
<font color="yellow">'For where the home is,</font>
<font color="yellow">there lies hope.</font>

58:00.800 --> 58:02.960
<font color="yellow">'And a future waits.</font>

58:04.600 --> 58:06.360
<font color="yellow">'And everything is possible.'</font>

58:17.880 --> 58:20.480
<font color="white">Engine trouble? Fetch a whip</font>
<font color="white">and thrash it like a horse!</font>

58:20.480 --> 58:22.320
<font color="yellow">Jimmy!</font>

58:22.320 --> 58:24.720
<font color="white">I thought there might be some</font>
<font color="white">lucky chap on the scene,</font>

58:24.720 --> 58:26.880
<font color="white">making your heart beat faster,</font>
<font color="white">all of that.</font>

58:26.880 --> 58:28.280
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

58:28.280 --> 58:29.280
<font color="white">I wrote to you.</font>

58:29.280 --> 58:32.400
<font color="white">I don't know if I said too much.</font>

58:32.400 --> 58:34.000
<font color="white">'Or not enough?'</font>

58:34.000 --> 58:37.480
<font color="yellow">Come on, Chummy! On the bed.</font>
<font color="yellow">High, hot and a hell of a lot!</font>

58:37.480 --> 58:39.040
<font color="cyan">No. No. You absolute beasts!</font>

58:39.040 --> 58:40.760
<font color="yellow">Is there any news? </font><font color="white">It's a baby,</font>

58:40.760 --> 58:43.960
<font color="white">not a lubricated penguin.</font>
<font color="white">They don't come sliding out to order.</font>

58:43.960 --> 58:46.400
<font color="white"># Oh, oh, baby</font>

58:46.400 --> 58:51.320
<font color="white"># I love you, oh baby, I do</font>

58:51.320 --> 58:54.640
<font color="white"># Baby, oh, baby</font>

58:54.640 --> 58:59.000
<font color="white"># Why don't you be true?</font>

58:59.000 --> 59:01.200
<font color="white"># Baby, oh, baby</font>

59:01.200 --> 59:04.800
<font color="white"># There is nothing I wouldn't do</font>

59:04.800 --> 59:07.040
<font color="white"># For you. #</font>

